item.title: Error
item.dc:creator: @sk8rdude461 sk8rdude461
item.description:
@sk8rdude461 wrote:

runescape sucks:

Well, I think with the run.bat error it is because you’re only supposed to use powers of 2 (I.E. 256, 512, 1024), but I could be wrong.

You are wrong, sorry.

Javac doesn’t use the -Xmx flag
-Xmx is to set the maximum allocated memory for the JVM.
Remove that from the compiler.

And as for eclipse, yes, you didn’t open the entire project…
http://www.rune-server.org/runescape-development/rs-503-client-server/tutorials/448938-how-load-rsps-through-eclipse-extreme-beginners-tutorial-1-a.html
